    {
      "sceneId": "scene2",
      "sceneName": "什么是益生菌",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "什么是益生菌？",
          "audioDuration": 1.8,
          "durationInFrames": 63,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene2/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "副标题",
          "text": "肠道里的「好帮手」",
          "audioDuration": 2.136,
          "durationInFrames": 74,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene2/02_副标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "概念解析",
          "audioDuration": 1.656,
          "durationInFrames": 59,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene2/03_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "益生菌就是对人体有益的活性微生物，住在肠道里，帮助消化、增强免疫力。简单说，就是宝宝肚子里的「小卫士」，专门打击坏细菌。",
          "audioDuration": 12.648,
          "durationInFrames": 389,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene2/04_正文.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene3",
      "sceneName": "宝宝需要补充吗",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "宝宝需要补充益生菌吗？",
          "audioDuration": 2.352,
          "durationInFrames": 80,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "副标题",
          "text": "不是所有宝宝都需要",
          "audioDuration": 2.4,
          "durationInFrames": 81,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/02_副标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "真相",
          "audioDuration": 1.296,
          "durationInFrames": 48,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/03_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "健康的宝宝，肠道菌群是平衡的，不需要额外补充。但如果宝宝腹泻、便秘、吃了抗生素，或者经常胀气，这时候益生菌才派上用场。",
          "audioDuration": 13.128,
          "durationInFrames": 403,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/04_正文.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "误区",
          "audioDuration": 1.248,
          "durationInFrames": 47,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/05_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "很多家长以为益生菌是「补品」，多吃多健康。其实盲目补充，反而可能打乱肠道平衡，适得其反。",
          "audioDuration": 9.48,
          "durationInFrames": 294,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene3/06_正文.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene4",
      "sceneName": "什么情况需要补",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "什么情况需要补充？",
          "audioDuration": 2.184,
          "durationInFrames": 75,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "副标题",
          "text": "对症下药才有效",
          "audioDuration": 2.184,
          "durationInFrames": 75,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/02_副标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "腹泻期间。拉肚子会冲走好菌，补充益生菌可以加快恢复。",
          "audioDuration": 6.408,
          "durationInFrames": 202,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/03_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "抗生素之后。抗生素「杀敌一千自损八百」，吃完要补充益生菌重建菌群。",
          "audioDuration": 7.584,
          "durationInFrames": 237,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/04_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "消化不良。经常胀气、便秘的宝宝，可以尝试益生菌调节。",
          "audioDuration": 6.24,
          "durationInFrames": 197,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/05_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "过敏体质。研究表明，某些菌株可能对湿疹等过敏症状有帮助。",
          "audioDuration": 6.792,
          "durationInFrames": 213,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene4/06_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene5",
      "sceneName": "如何选择益生菌",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "如何选择益生菌？",
          "audioDuration": 2.184,
          "durationInFrames": 75,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "副标题",
          "text": "看这4个关键指标",
          "audioDuration": 2.232,
          "durationInFrames": 76,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/02_副标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "菌株",
          "audioDuration": 1.248,
          "durationInFrames": 47,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/03_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "认准菌株号，如鼠李糖乳杆菌LGG、罗伊氏乳杆菌DSM17938，这些是有临床验证的明星菌株。",
          "audioDuration": 10.368,
          "durationInFrames": 321,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/04_正文.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "活菌数",
          "audioDuration": 1.512,
          "durationInFrames": 55,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/05_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "保质期内活菌数至少10亿CFU以上。注意是「保质期末」的数量，不是生产时的数量。",
          "audioDuration": 8.544,
          "durationInFrames": 266,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/06_正文.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 7,
          "type": "小标题",
          "text": "配料表",
          "audioDuration": 1.464,
          "durationInFrames": 53,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/07_小标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 8,
          "type": "正文",
          "text": "越简单越好。避免添加糖、香精、色素。麦芽糊精作为载体是可以接受的。",
          "audioDuration": 8.352,
          "durationInFrames": 260,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene5/08_正文.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene6",
      "sceneName": "常见误区",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "家长常踩的3个坑",
          "audioDuration": 2.352,
          "durationInFrames": 80,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene6/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "副标题",
          "text": "你中了几个？",
          "audioDuration": 1.68,
          "durationInFrames": 60,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene6/02_副标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "热水冲泡。超过40度会杀死益生菌，请用温水或凉白开冲泡。",
          "audioDuration": 6.984,
          "durationInFrames": 219,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene6/03_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "和抗生素同时吃。抗生素会杀死益生菌，要间隔至少2小时服用。",
          "audioDuration": 7.296,
          "durationInFrames": 228,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene6/04_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "type": "卡片标题+内容",
          "text": "买贵的就是好的。价格和效果不成正比，关键看菌株和活菌数。",
          "audioDuration": 6.696,
          "durationInFrames": 210,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene6/05_卡片标题_内容.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene7",
      "sceneName": "服用建议",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "标题",
          "text": "正确服用小贴士",
          "audioDuration": 2.184,
          "durationInFrames": 75,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/01_标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "type": "策略标题",
          "text": "温度控制",
          "audioDuration": 1.584,
          "durationInFrames": 57,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/02_策略标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "type": "策略内容",
          "text": "用37度左右的温水冲泡，冲好后尽快喝完，别放置太久。",
          "audioDuration": 6.0,
          "durationInFrames": 189,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/03_策略内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "type": "策略标题",
          "text": "最佳时间",
          "audioDuration": 1.632,
          "durationInFrames": 58,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/04_策略标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "type": "策略内容",
          "text": "饭后30分钟服用最佳，此时胃酸最低，益生菌存活率更高。",
          "audioDuration": 6.264,
          "durationInFrames": 197,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/05_策略内容.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "type": "策略标题",
          "text": "疗程建议",
          "audioDuration": 1.656,
          "durationInFrames": 59,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/06_策略标题.mp3"
        },
        {
          "order": 7,
          "type": "策略内容",
          "text": "一般服用2-4周即可，不需要长期吃。如果症状改善，可以逐渐减量停止。",
          "audioDuration": 7.656,
          "durationInFrames": 239,
          "audioFile": "/audio/babyProbiotics/scene7/07_策略内容.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "scene8",
      "sceneName": "结尾",
      "items": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "type": "名言",
          "text": "益生菌不是万能药，也不是必需品。科学选择，按需补充，才是对宝宝最好的爱。",
          "audioDuration": 8.04,
